OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Rosemary Mair to Sabbhineni Meghana, 0 run(s),  WICKET Sabbhineni Meghana c Katey Martin b Rosemary Mair (India Women 100 Runs for 1 wicket). A fantastic innings from Meghana comes to an end as Rosemary Mair gets the breakthrough for New Zealand! Banged in short of good length and down leg, Meghana tries to pull but gets an edge that goes through safely to Katey Martin.
Sabbhineni Meghana gave India a blazing start in the Powerplay, taking full advantage of the field restrictions. 79% (48/61) of her runs have come through boundaries!
